cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DC

The paper discusses the impact of reputation on decision-making in distributed electronic environments, which involves concepts related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and distributed computing (cs.DC). The focus on virtual marketplaces and the cognitive theory of reputation suggests a connection to complex systems (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
